{"tid":1554900,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［不分化純討論］老豆老母對破壞中環站有嘢講","createTime":"2019-09-09T07:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T10:43:23.000Z","uid":133422,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"953b4bfe254aa5c47c400d41b887e4910d506c24","tid":1554900,"uid":133422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"首先要交代一吓屋企背景先<br />\n老豆老母係深黃，重點佢地係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逐漸變深</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始會覺得衝擊立法會過激<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來佢地明白前線嘅目的後係表示理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到近日，已經發展到覺得就算上次斬退休警單嘢係前線做，都絕對唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但尋日佢地睇到中環站放火爆玻璃<br />\n老豆開始問<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解要爆玻璃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n老母問<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登有無人討論地鐵站應該破壞到咩程度</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後老豆再補多句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係擔心啲玻璃爛，而係咁樣意義不大。我係擔心前線破壞期間俾黑警捉，走唔切就慘</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上分享唔係想割蓆，其實之前打爆咗咁多部入閘機，老豆老母係無意見，因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">知道係有咩目的</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但打爆玻璃放火其實真係無咩成效，加上文宣不足，群眾會覺得為破壞而破壞，出師無名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再話唔需要理民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">呢場係群眾運動，群眾嘅支持就係我地最大嘅武器同力量</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574d8ec8ce888915f25fa10f8cd381de721dc69a","tid":1554900,"uid":133422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"33262051ba1bfe8dd285ccdee49b8c034d6e23f1","tid":1554900,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"no one cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1c48ad44a64e535d9aa4a63cc6d82cd81b7039","tid":1554900,"uid":229385,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"放火係外國人眼中覺得好少事"},{"pid":"c42552d7d8d91aa19fa886d8e876110ffbc0fe59","tid":1554900,"uid":274435,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:06:20.000Z","msg":"其實啲人都唔係好care破壞黨鐵<br />\n又唔係納稅人錢<br />\n第朝一樣返到工"},{"pid":"e18b144fe7774400a4392fd157839b60c4800c8a","tid":1554900,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91d308e3df6e968c28e39e6fcede4354eeaf025d","tid":1554900,"uid":133422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ee1c48ad44a64e535d9aa4a63cc6d82cd81b7039","tid":1554900,"uid":229385,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"放火係外國人眼中覺得好少事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:07:30.0