站，驚ｄ狗搭黨鐵一車車咁黎中環捉人，所以set rb塞住個入口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"我老母都有問我係狗開拖先定set rb先<br />\n我老母因爲有我解釋所以知咩事<br />\n<br />\n但未必全香港人都知，新聞又無講得好清楚<br />\n無可否認，呢排文宣係少咗"},{"pid":"3ed0f513ba6c6e2fe31b83f2acf5dac3f606d895","tid":1554900,"uid":284636,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91d308e3df6e968c28e39e6fcede4354eeaf025d","tid":1554900,"uid":133422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ee1c48ad44a64e535d9aa4a63cc6d82cd81b7039","tid":1554900,"uid":229385,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:06:00.000Z","msg":"放火係外國人眼中覺得好少事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"香港人唔同<br />\n就算開咗閘，大家都係照排隊嘟八達通<br />\n其實呢幾個月香港人嘅思想已經進化緊，但真係要時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"其實勇武捱得咁辛苦<br />\n才等和理非思想漸漸進化<br />\n可悲涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023cdfa14340d9c03b366d01af3154270c0e0dd8","tid":1554900,"uid":133422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41d31ef09645e442ead714ae50993fb56a6c00b1","tid":1554900,"uid":300783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"我就覺得集中爆閘機幾好，好強嘅訊息。其他就唔洗化時間專登爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"同感<br />\n藍絲應該邊鬧邊希望可以免費撘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2c1fa158f4421b07e2cf7ebdc0df414f6c1bb2","tid":1554900,"uid":133422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ed0f513ba6c6e2fe31b83f2acf5dac3f606d895","tid":1554900,"uid":284636,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91d308e3df6e968c28e39e6fcede4354eeaf025d","tid":1554900,"uid":133422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ee1c48ad44a64e535d9aa4a63cc6d82cd81b7039","tid"